comments: Jokic (DEN) is in the lane for less than three seconds before the imminent shot attempt.
Bjelica (SAC) makes contact with Millsap's (DEN) arm after his gather and affects his driving shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) and Barton (DEN) engage and disengage during the rebound. As Barton is coming down with the rebound he makes incidental contact with Millsap (DEN).
Holmes (SAC) makes contact to Barton's (DEN) upper body and affects his body's trajectory during the shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in the path of Harris (DEN).
Jokic (DEN) engages with Holmes (SAC) during the shot and does not affect his ability to rebound.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Harris (DEN).
Holmes (SAC) does not establish himself in a legal guarding position and makes contact to Barton's (DEN) body at the end of the drive.
Barton (DEN) is in the restricted area when he makes body contact with Holmes (SAC) during his driving dunk attempt.
Murray (DEN) makes marginal contact with Fox (SAC) during the drive but does not affect his ability to defend.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Grant (DEN).
Hield (SAC) makes contact to Harris (DEN) in the backcourt and commits a take foul.
Murray (DEN) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Barnes (SAC) off ball.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
Barnes (SAC) cleanly dislodges the ball from Grant (DEN) during the rebound.
